title: 820-3662-A - MacBook Pro 15" High Fan Spin
message:
Check R5426 and its traces.
Post U5420 output voltage.

title: 820-3662-A - MacBook Pro 15" High Fan Spin
message:
U5420 ouput: 0.11V
R5426 is fine, 4.4K

checked also ouput of U5430: 0.09V

title: 820-3662-A - MacBook Pro 15" High Fan Spin
message:
Not sure, but looks very low.
You should compare with good board.
5A is the max current designed for R5420 and the output should be aprox 2.5V in such case.
Considering 2-3A as normal consumption, I'll expect 1-1.5V at C5426.

title: 820-3662-A - MacBook Pro 15" High Fan Spin
message:
just checked. no good board to compare.

same voltage on C5426. Voltage is starting from 0.03 to 0.11 while the fans getting faster.

title: 820-3662-A - MacBook Pro 15" High Fan Spin
message:
No need exact the same board.
Check the equivalent signal on other MacBook Pro board.
